commentText: Set the mappings of bean keys to a comma-separated list of method names._The property key should match the bean key and the property value should match_the list of method names. When searching for method names for a bean, Spring_will check these mappings first._@param mappings the mappins of bean keys to method names
codeText: public void setMethodMappings(Properties mappings) {_		this.methodMappings = new HashMap<String, Set<String>>()__		for (Enumeration en = mappings.keys()_ en.hasMoreElements()_) {_			String beanKey = (String) en.nextElement()__			String[] methodNames = StringUtils.commaDelimitedListToStringArray(mappings.getProperty(beanKey))__			this.methodMappings.put(beanKey, new HashSet<String>(Arrays.asList(methodNames)))__		}_	}
